verbose_text: The data obtained from 94 neurons showed that incubation of the CGNs with 10, 100 and 300 ng/ml GDF15 for 24 h increased the current densities by -2.2% (n = 27), 37.7% (from 761.07 +/-38.22 pA to 1048.40 +/-40.25 pA; n = 41; P> 0.05) and 45.6% (n = 26) respectively (XREF_FIG A and XREF_FIG B).
